{"tid":2373498,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤16年後圓《頭文字D》夢揸GTR 自嘲︰能死不能輸，買不得","createTime":"2021-01-20T13:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T13:30:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d48c05f0ac11ee485b98066e734582c6eee3636","tid":2373498,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/242SAC3NVeQU_yLzds17bnJ4keM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K26XWMJ34BAX7MQMNMNTQIXIII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F242SAC3NVeQU_yLzds17bnJ4keM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK26XWMJ34BAX7MQMNMNTQIXIII.jpg&h=52f16b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤2005年演出漫畫改編電影《頭文字D》，他在戲中飾演油站少東阿木。雖然主角是周杰倫演的藤原拓海，不過有網民覺得阿澤才是男主角，他在戲中同老竇鍾鎮濤的對話「我要買GTR」、「你噚晚爭啲死噃」、「我噚晚如果揸GTR，我使炒」、「你揸GTR，死咗嘞」同「小心甩尾呀」，成為不少討論區常用的金句。阿澤在拍完《頭》片後，買了一輛戲中拓海的戰車AE86，事隔16年，阿澤終於在台灣一圓阿木「心願」揸GTR。<br />\n<br />\n阿澤目前身在台灣，為自家收費台節目《尋找他媽的故事》拍攝。今日他在台中精明一街扮演街頭廚神，吸引不少人排隊等食。昨日他在facebook留言話終於可以「揸GTR」，他留言：「說了這麼多年，今天終於第一次開GTR。感謝台中的兄弟幫忙！台中就是超跑多，兄弟多！」阿澤自言好勝心重「只能死不能輸」，所以這類動輒時速都爆錶的跑車，最好都是不要買、不要開。他說揸GTR感覺是「油門一踏下去，腦袋馬上失控，珍惜生命，是對愛你的人的一個責任。浮生若夢，開心過就好。」<br />\n<br />\n阿澤所講的「GTR」其實是車迷對日產Skyliner GT-R的簡稱。1989代號RB32的GTR面世，當時以無敵姿態橫掃各大賽事，而贏得「戰神」美譽，跑車迷都趨之若鶩。所以《頭文字D》漫畫當時都加入此車款，電影中由余文樂飾演的中里毅駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210120/LQS7P6IZDJDNLDM3KIG5CBEPME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210120%2FLQS7P6IZDJDNLDM3KIG5CBEPME%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IaxlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=cc0d4e4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210120%2FLQS7P6IZDJDNLDM3KIG5CBEPME%2F&h=efb57eab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210120/LQS7P6IZDJDNLDM3KIG5CBEPME/</a>"},{"pid":"e721fa2ce7855895113ae28b0e593609b8657b4e","tid":2373498,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"我要買GTR！<br />\n我買BENZ俾你丫。<br />\n我要買GTR！<br />\n加隻「撈」。<br />\n我要買GTR！<br />\n但係你尋晚差D死啵。<br />\n我尋晚如果揸GTR 我使炒？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f02ab9306cd376211f235a5560b0a50c6119079","tid":2373498,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"我揸車 你洗車<br />\n幾有前途呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2ef9a98bda1a22f86f2053b579e84abf41b562","tid":2373498,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"佢收哂錢肯開台未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879943095e319007d7eafc4be6144a8be0578869","tid":2373498,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"高橋涼介，你幾時同我走返轉呀？"},{"pid":"03bf9a8326990c7f6a893bb79a57213818929c6a","tid":2373498,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e721fa2ce7855895113ae28b0e593609b8657b4e","tid":2373498,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"我要買GTR！<br />\n我買BENZ俾你丫。<br />\n我要買GTR！<br />\n加隻「撈」。<br />\n我要買GTR！<br />\n但係你尋晚差D死啵。<br />\n我尋晚如果揸GTR 我使炒？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"你渣GTR你死左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk